'''Epiphany''' is  simple, fast Webkit web browser for [[GNOME]].

== Installation ==
Install {{Package|www-client/epiphany}}:
{{USEflag|package=www-client/epiphany
|avahi
|debug
|doc
|introspection
|networkmanager
|nss
}}

{{Emerge|epiphany}}

== Flash support ==
Install {{Package|www-plugins/adobe-flash}} and {{Package|www-plugins/nspluginwrapper}}:
{{Emerge|adobe-flash nspluginwrapper}}
 
Execute the following command to get flash working in Epiphany (on 32 bit): 
{{RootCmd|/usr/lib/nspluginwrapper/i386/linux/npconfig -v -a -n -i}}

For 64 bit, change ''i386'' in the previous command to ''x86_64''.

